                    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Privacy Policy</h2>
                    <p>Welcome to <strong>ClayHaven</strong>. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when using our platform to purchase handcrafted clay designs.</p>

                    <h4 class="mt-4"><i class="bi bi-people"></i> 1. Information We Collect</h4>
