                        <li>Secure payment processors to handle transactions.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>Your data is protected with <strong>encryption, firewalls, and strict access controls</strong>.</p>

                    <h4 class="mt-4"><i class="bi bi-cookie"></i> 4. Cookies & Tracking</h4>
