                    <ul>
                        <li>Enhance website functionality.</li>
                        <li>Analyze shopping behavior for better recommendations.</li>
                        <li>Remember your preferences and saved items.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>You can disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>

                    <h4 class="mt-4"><i class="bi bi-person-check"></i> 5. Your Rights & Choices</h4>
